				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\text{K}/\text{S }=\frac{{(1-{\varvec{R}})}^{2}}{2{\varvec{R}}}-\frac{{(1-{{\varvec{R}}}_{{\varvec{o}}})}^{2}}{{2{\varvec{R}}}_{{\varvec{o}}}}$$\end{document}where R denotes reflectance, K denotes absorption coefficient, and S denotes scattering coefficient.

